description:
The RDA Entity properties element set consists of properties representing elements of the RDA *Entity* entity.

Version: 1.0.0

P00001.label: has related RDA entity of RDA entity
P00001.description: Relates an RDA entity to an RDA entity that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00002.label: has related work of RDA entity
P00002.description: Relates an RDA entity to a work that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00003.label: has related expression of RDA entity
P00003.description: Relates an RDA entity to an expression that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00004.label: has related manifestation of RDA entity
P00004.description: Relates an RDA entity to a manifestation that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00005.label: has related item of RDA entity
P00005.description: Relates an RDA entity to an item that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00006.label: has related agent of RDA entity
P00006.description: Relates an RDA entity to an agent who is associated with an RDA entity.

P00007.label: has related person of RDA entity
P00007.description: Relates an RDA entity to a person who is associated with an RDA entity.

P00008.label: has related family of RDA entity
P00008.description: Relates an RDA entity to a family who is associated with an RDA entity.

P00009.label: has related corporate body of RDA entity
P00009.description: Relates an RDA entity to a corporate body who is associated with an RDA entity.

P00010.label: has related place of RDA entity
P00010.description: Relates an RDA entity to a place that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00011.label: has related timespan of RDA entity
P00011.description: Relates an RDA entity to a timespan that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00012.label: has related collective agent of RDA entity
P00012.description: Relates an RDA entity to a collective agent who is associated with an RDA entity.

P00013.label: has related nomen of RDA entity
P00013.description: Relates an RDA entity to a nomen that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00014.label: is subject RDA entity of
P00014.description: Relates an RDA entity to a work that is about an RDA entity.

P00015.label: has note on RDA entity
P00015.description: Relates an RDA entity to a broad unstructured description of one or more attributes of an RDA entity.

P00016.label: has access point for RDA entity
P00016.description: Relates an RDA entity to an appellation of RDA entity in natural language that is taken from a vocabulary encoding scheme or is constructed using a string encoding scheme.

P00017.label: has appellation of RDA entity
P00017.description: Relates an RDA entity to a nomen that is used within a given scheme or context to refer to an RDA entity.

P00018.label: has identifier for RDA entity
P00018.description: Relates an RDA entity to an appellation of RDA entity that consists of a code, number, or other string, usually independent of natural language and social naming conventions, used to identify an RDA entity.

P00019.label: has name of RDA entity
P00019.description: Relates an RDA entity to an appellation of RDA entity in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

P00020.label: has authorized access point for RDA entity
P00020.description: Relates an RDA entity to an access point for RDA entity that is selected for preference in a specific vocabulary encoding scheme.

P00021.label: has preferred name of RDA entity
P00021.description: Relates an RDA entity to a name of RDA entity that is selected for preference in a specific application or context.

P00022.label: has variant access point for RDA entity
P00022.description: Relates an RDA entity to an access point for RDA entity that is not selected for preference in a specific vocabulary encoding scheme.

P00023.label: has variant name of RDA entity
P00023.description: Relates an RDA entity to a name of RDA entity that is not selected for preference in a specific application or context.

P00024.label: is RDA entity critiqued in
P00024.description: Relates an RDA entity to a work that contains a critical evaluation of a described RDA entity.

P00025.label: is RDA entity described in
P00025.description: Relates an RDA entity to a work that describes a described RDA entity.

P00026.label: is RDA entity evaluated in
P00026.description: Relates an RDA entity to a work that examines or judges a described RDA entity.

P00027.label: is RDA entity reviewed in
P00027.description: Relates an RDA entity to a work that contains a brief evaluation of a described RDA entity.

P00028.label: has related entity of RDA entity
P00028.description: Relates an RDA entity to an entity that is associated with an RDA entity.

P00029.label: has category of RDA entity
P00029.description: Relates an RDA entity to a type to which an RDA entity belongs.
